Among Us Dumpy Bot BOT 12-Oct-21 03:22 PM
My commands!
Made by ThatOneCalculator#1337 and Dsim64#8145! () = optional, <> = mandatory.
!!dumpy (height) (@person)
Makes a dumpy gif from whatever image you post, whatever image was the latest in chat, or from a person's avatar. Height can be a number between 2 and 35, the default is 10. If you tag a person after the height, it will use their avatar instead of the last image in chat.
!!furry (height) (@person)
The same as !!dumpy, but uses a furry template, UwU~ (Template by twistCMYK)
!!background (option)
Set a custom background image for !!dumpy and !!furry. Run !!background delete to remove your current background, run !!background color for a solid color, !!background #AAAAAA for a custom color background, !!background flag for pride flags (gay, lesbian, trans, etc) and run !!background and attach an image for a custom image as a background.
!!text <text>
Writes something out, but sus.
!!tall <number>
Makes a tall sussy imposter!
!!ping
Pings the bot, and gives some information.
!!topgg
Check the number of votes on top.gg, and vote for the bot.
!!statcord
Brings you to the bot's statcord page.
!!literallynobot
Directs you to ThatOneCalculator's main bot LiterallyNoBot.
Tips and tricks
- You can add nodumpy to a channel topic to disable the bot there. - If you need more lines, go to the GitHub and use the desktop version.
